window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Since being trapped in Sky Realms Online, Hall has been tested.</b></p> <p>The game has changed multiple times. He's faced demons and new races. He's found love and a town to make a home in. He's found friends and companions, discovering that there is more to the NPCs than previously thought.</p> <p>But he's also found questions. Why is the game changing? Who are the Champions?</p> <p>Hall and his friends, along with some new allies and even old enemies, will find the answers to their questions through the Onyxgate. But in a contest between titanic powers, can there truly be a winner? Even if he wins, will things ever be the same again? And if he loses, is the fate of two worlds at risk?</p> <p><b>The thrilling sixth and final installment of the Sky Realms Online LitRPG Series is finally here! Grab your copy today.</b></p>"; 
